fields.description:
I'd like to be able to do:

{code:xml}
<Alloy>
  <Label text="L('key') :" />
</Alloy>
{code}

Currently this compiles to:

{code:js}
    $.__views.__alloyId0 = Ti.UI.createLabel({
        text: 'L("time") :',
        id: "__alloyId0"
    });
{code}

While I'd like it to be:

{code:js}
    $.__views.__alloyId0 = Ti.UI.createLabel({
        text: L("time") + ' :',
        id: "__alloyId0"
    });
{code}
